msquerybuilderbackend.entity

Class Relationship

  • java.lang.Object
    • msquerybuilderbackend.entity.Relationship

  • public class Relationship
extends java.lang.Object
    entity class of Relationship with getter and setter Relationship is an entity used in the entity node in the QueryBuilder object and consists of ReturnAttributes, FilterAttributes, OrderByAttributes and the Node (and also some metadata) the entity is relevant for parsing the QueryBuilderObject and interpreting it
